Bodie Olmos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bodie_Olmos 0 Bodie James Olmos (born August 27, 1975) is an American actor. He is the son of Edward James Olmos and Katija Keel, and grandson of Howard Keel.His older brother is actor Mico Olmos, and his younger sister is Daniela Olmos. His first on screen appearance was on The Ballad of Gregorio Cortez in 1982 when he was 7 years old. His most recent appearance on television is alongside his father in Battlestar Galactica as Lieutenant Junior Grade Brendan "Hotdog" Costanza. He also acted in a film directed by his father named Walkout. Bodie_James_Olmos ( born August_27_,_1975 ) is an_American_actor .
